{"tid":2214424,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[FYK] 《潛龍諜影》等經典遊戲 PC 版資料被登錄在台灣分級網站","createTime":"2020-09-23T08:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:46.000Z","uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2321b600d6f20d528b6a27c2bc89d7f88c7ad6d","tid":2214424,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"Source: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=203659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D203659&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=d3731d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=203659</a><br />\n<br />\nlink入面有圖，大家自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三款《潛龍諜影》系列與《KONAMI 精選集系列：惡魔城和魂斗羅（Konami Collector's Series: Castlevania and Contra）》PC 遊戲資料在台灣分級網站上被登錄，目前消息尚不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n國外媒體於台灣分級網站發現，初代《潛龍諜影》、《潛龍諜影 2：真實之影》、《KONAMI 精選集系列：惡魔城和魂斗羅》共四款遊戲被新登錄在數位娛樂軟體分級查詢網上，遊戲平台為 PC 單機，目前上市時間未定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而根據頁面上的遊戲簡介描述，玩家似乎將有機會可以再次回溫這幾款遊戲。而究竟遊戲將是調整後再次推出，還是 HD 化等尚不確定，確切消息仍待官方證實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"0c3c1e68ed724e1c96c8c886660bed5315d70cba","tid":2214424,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}